Text: Does not work on a Sprint iPhone 4S. It says there is a compatibility issue. Any suggestions?

@cristina.ashley That's because this is for GSM networks such as AT&T or T-mobile. Verizon and Sprint iPhones are not supported by this version. However, you may be able to find a CDMA (Verizon, Sprint) version elsewhere on TPB.
